mer days that predom inate in September October and in the South November A natural solution is comfortable cotton dresses of plaid gingham solid color chantbray and checked suit ing that are equally at ease in the classroom or office Both business girls and college students are considering careful ly what clothes will take them through a productive year with the least expense Dark cotton dirndls are a must for the miss with economy in mind for they can be worn with a whole ward robe of cotton blouses Some skirts come with inset bands of white cotton eyelet which makes them perfect companions to sheer batiste dropshoulder blouses that are booked for party wear this fall Shirttails are tucked neat ly out of sight under slim skirts this year Jackets are boxy dis tinguished by Chinese collars and i i__ rpu _ frnnf liaicu cardigan is still holding its own in sports types with contrasting binding in dressy"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2023-08-12T17:37:38.715Z", "group": ["ndnp/ncu", "university-of-north-carolina-chapel-hill-library-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/2017236974/1945-08-30/ed-1/?sp=4", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ncu:batch_ncu_kale_ver01:data:2017236974:00279558078:1945083001:0774/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=340&w=224", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ncu:batch_ncu_kale_ver01:data:2017236974:00279558078:1945083001:0774/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=680&w=448", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/ncu/batch_ncu_kale_ver01/data/2017236974/00279558078/1945083001/0774.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "location": ["halifax", "halifax county", "north carolina", "roanoke rapids", "united states"], "location_city": ["roanoke rapids"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["halifax"], "location_state": ["north carolina"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application